Fresh off the heels of getting his wisdom teeth removed (https://youtu.be/FOKS19r2Hqs), Carter Sharer and Team RAR has one of the biggest reveals ever done on YouTube: presenting the new Team RAR house!! Everyone on Team RAR was flown out to an undisclosed location to see the incredible new house, including: Lizzy Capri, Ryan Prunty, Stove's Kitchen, Bailey Bagles Payne, Deniesse, Matt Braeden, Elena, Ethan, Casey, Ben, Andrew, Matt, Ashley, Phil, Jep, Panos and of course Millie. But this reveal is bitter-sweet because while Team RAR will be moving on to an awesome new house, it means we're having to leave the awesome Team RAR mansion in Los Angeles. We've made a lot of incredible memories and great videos in this house, from the world-record trampoline tower stack, to an entire Lego city, to countless 100 button mystery box challenges and tons of Last to Leave videos for insane prizes like Lamborghinis or $10,000. This house has been good to us (despite the occasional attic hauntings), but now it's time to start a new chapter for Team RAR. What would you like to see next?? Comment below!!
